'''Before the Helmet''' was a feature on [[Hyperspace: The Official Star Wars Fan Club|Hyperspace: The Official ''Star Wars'' Fan Club]] that showed production photos of [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|''Star Wars'': Episode III ''Revenge of the Sith'']]. Before the Helmet began on [[October 2]], [[2003]] with the image "I Sense Much Fear in You" and ended [[May 18]], [[2005]] with "The Helmet Lowers". The photo gallery contained eighty-three pictures.

==StarWars.com summary==
''For the first time on a ''Star Wars'' film, [[StarWars.com]] is pleased to present an online gallery of production photos released before the film hits the theaters. A Hyperspace members exclusive!''

